#~ "server <systemitem role=\"package\">zope</systemitem> sau <systemitem "
#~ "role=\"package\">plone</systemitem>. Deși Plone include un utilitar de "
#~ "migrare, experiența arată că migrările automate pot da greș foarte ușor."

# type: Content of: <chapter><section><para>
#~ msgid ""
#~ "For this reason, users are recommended to set up their system so they can "
#~ "continue to run the &oldreleasename; installation of Zope/Plone alongside "
